S&P 500 Futures Extend Gains, Rising 0.6% to 1,226

-- B y   S h a n i   R a j a
-- 
2011-10-17T02:49:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-17/s-p-500-futures-extend-gains-rising-0-6-to-1-226.html
Futures on the Standard & Poor’s 500
Index extended gains, rising 0.6 percent to 1,226 as of 11:49
a.m. Tokyo time. Group of 20 finance chiefs meeting in Paris at
the weekend endorsed parts of a plan to contain  Europe ’s debt
crisis.  To contact the reporter on this story:
